title: God Shave the Queens
overview: Prepare yourself for God Shave the Queens! Each episode features the queens on the road during the RuPaul's Drag Race UK European tour and the events that occur at each destination they head to. So, what happens when you mix The Vivienne, Davina De Campo, Baga Chipz, Cheryl Hole, Blu Hydrangea, Crystal, Sum Ting Wong, Vinegar Strokes, Scaredy Kat, Gothy Kendoll â€“ and Alyssa Edwards, who emceed the tour? You'll just have to find out for yourself, but spoiler alert: it's THAT good!
